       Name: Overwhelming Assault
       Kind: Skill
     Target: TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE
   Position: POS_FIGHTING
   Min Mana: 80
 Wait Beats: 24
 Can Learn: TRUE
Noun Damage: Overwhelming Assault
   Wear-Off: None
Acquisition:
   - Crusader: level 15
Description:
   Overwhelming Assault is an alternative combo finisher that replaces the
   normal combo burst trigger. When the combo sequence is ready for a
   finisher (all but the last slot filled with unique war_attack skills),
   using Overwhelming Assault delivers a single devastating blow instead
   of the normal random-attack burst.

   Requires: is_valid_finisher(ch) == TRUE (combo at max-1 slots filled)
   Resets combo on use.
   Cooldown: 20 rounds
   Damage element: Physical
   Damage formula: war_attack base damage * combo_damage_multiplier
                   * (10 + Crusader level) / 10

   This gives Crusaders a deliberate choice: normal combo trigger (many
   random hits + stun chance) vs. Overwhelming Assault (one enormous hit).
   The lore's "decisive finishing blows" doctrine made mechanical --
   channeling all accumulated momentum into a single overwhelming impact.

   Works with the combo system: uses get_max_combo(), reset_combo(),
   is_valid_finisher(), and combo_damage_multiplier_for_max_combo().
*******************************************************************************
